sequenceDiagram
    participant User as User / DSP Operator
    participant K8sAPI as Kubernetes API<br/>443/TCP HTTPS TLS 1.2+
    participant WFC as workflow-controller<br/>informers + reconciler
    participant Pod as Workflow Pod
    participant ArgoExec as argoexec (sidecar)<br/>emissary pattern
    participant S3 as S3 / Minio<br/>443/TCP HTTPS
    participant PG as PostgreSQL<br/>5432/TCP TLS

    rect rgb(220, 240, 255)
        Note over User,PG: Flow 1: Workflow Execution
        User->>K8sAPI: Create Workflow CR<br/>Auth: ServiceAccount Bearer
        K8sAPI-->>WFC: Informer watch event<br/>TLS 1.2+
        WFC->>K8sAPI: Create Pod (main + argoexec)<br/>Auth: ServiceAccount Bearer
        K8sAPI-->>Pod: Pod scheduled & started

        Note over ArgoExec: Init Container Phase
        ArgoExec->>S3: Download input artifacts<br/>Auth: AccessKey/SecretKey
        S3-->>ArgoExec: Artifact data

        Note over Pod: Main container executes

        Note over ArgoExec: Wait/Sidecar Phase
        ArgoExec->>S3: Upload output artifacts<br/>Auth: AccessKey/SecretKey
        S3-->>ArgoExec: Upload confirmed
        ArgoExec->>K8sAPI: Patch WorkflowTaskResult<br/>Auth: ServiceAccount Bearer

        WFC->>K8sAPI: Update Workflow status
        WFC->>PG: Archive workflow (optional)<br/>Auth: Secret credentials
    end

    rect rgb(255, 240, 220)
        Note over User,PG: Flow 2: CronWorkflow Scheduling
        Note over WFC: Cron controller checks schedule
        WFC->>K8sAPI: List CronWorkflows<br/>Auth: ServiceAccount Bearer
        K8sAPI-->>WFC: CronWorkflow list
        WFC->>K8sAPI: Create Workflow from CronWorkflow<br/>Auth: ServiceAccount Bearer
    end

    rect rgb(255, 220, 220)
        Note over User,PG: Flow 3: Artifact Garbage Collection
        WFC->>K8sAPI: Create WorkflowArtifactGCTask<br/>Auth: ServiceAccount Bearer
        WFC->>K8sAPI: Create GC Pod<br/>Auth: ServiceAccount Bearer
        Note over ArgoExec: GC Pod (argoexec)
        ArgoExec->>S3: Delete expired artifacts<br/>Auth: AccessKey/SecretKey
    end
